Daily Investor is South Africa’s top investment news and analysis platform and has seen remarkable growth since it was launched in August 2022 by Broad Media. Its audience comprises 350,000 South African fund managers, analysts, finance professionals, and retail investors. Of these readers: Over 30,000 have created user profiles on the site.
Over 31,000 have signed up for the daily email newsletter. This rapid growth is thanks to the excellent content provided by Daily Investor, which allows investors to keep up-to-date with the latest news and trends. Keeping up to date with Daily Investor Daily Investor offers the latest investing insights and financial data, as well as a fresh perspective on large, medium, and small-cap companies listed on the Johannesburg Stock Exchange (JSE). It also covers international stocks – especially US equities – and provides insights into macroeconomic events and how they influence financial markets. Daily Investor supplements this reporting with well-researched feature articles – including pieces that highlight the stock picks of expert investors, as well as performance tracking of these prominent professionals. To find out more about Daily Investor, contact Broad Media CCO Kevin Lancaster.